
  List all available physical disks on the system.                                                                      
         
  USAGE  
         
    nbc list [--flags]  
         
  FLAGS  
         
    -n --dry-run  Dry run mode (no actual changes)
    -h --help     Help for list
    --json        Output in JSON format
    -s --silent   Suppress all progress output
    -v --verbose  Verbose output

